課程教材 Course Material
	    1.Black, J. M. & Hawks, J. H. (2009). Medical-surgical nursing: Clinical management for positive outcome (8th ed.). Philadelphia, PA: Elsevier Saunders.    

參考書目 References
	    1.Storch, J. E. (2005). Reconstructive plastic surgical nursing : clinical management and wound care. Malden, MA : Blackwell Publishing.
2.Smeltzer, S. C., & Bare, B. G. (2008). Brunner & Suddarth’s Textbook of Medical-Surgical Nursing (10th Ed). Philadelphia, PA: Lippincott Williams & Wilkins.
3.Stanley, M. & Beare, P. (2009).  Gerontological Nursing: Promoting Successful Aging with Older Adults. Philadelphia: F.A. Davis Company.
4.Touhy, T. & Jett, K. (2009). Gerontological Nursing and Healthy Aging (3rd Ed). St. Louis: Elsevier.
5.王世俊、林麗嬋、張文芸等合著(2010)•老年護理學•臺北華杏•
6.王靜枝、張文芸等合著(2008) •醫護另類療法•臺北:華騰•
7.胡月娟等合著（2005）•內外科護理學（上、下冊）•臺北：華杏•
8.高紀惠等合著（2005）•布氏內外科護理學（第一冊至第四冊）•臺北：藝軒•
9.葉淑惠、張文芸等合著（2009）•老人照護指引•臺北：華杏•
10.楊詠仁、張文芸等合著（2009）•失智老人照護指引•臺北：合記圖書出版社•    

